'''人體冷凍機構'''（{{lang-en|Cryonics Institute}}）是一間提供[[人體冷凍技術|人體冷凍]]服務的[[非牟利機構|非牟利機構]]，該機構是現時[[美國|美國]]第二大提供人體冷凍服務的供應商。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20160424-if-cryonics-suddenly-worked-wed-need-to-face-the-fallout|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230234043/https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20160424-if-cryonics-suddenly-worked-wed-need-to-face-the-fallout|archive-date=2019-12-30|title=If cryonics suddenly worked, we’d need to face the fallout|date=2016-04-24|newspaper=BBC|language=en|access-date=2020-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
人體冷凍機構創立於1976年，並在同年首次進行人體冷凍服務。現時人體冷凍機構機構的總部位於[[美國|美國]][[密歇根州|密歇根州]]。人體冷凍服務主要是為其會員在[[法律|法律]]上被宣佈[[死亡|死亡]]後，将[[遗体|遗体]]以[[液態氮|液態氮]]保存。人體冷凍機構由世界首位提出[[人體冷凍技術|人體冷凍技術]]概念的[[罗伯特·埃丁格|罗伯特·埃丁格]]成立。罗伯特·埃丁格於1962年出版了《The Prospect of Immortality》，提出以人體冷凍概念達到[[長生不老|長生不老]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/nov/18/the-cryonics-dilemma-will-deep-frozen-bodies-be-fit-for-new-life|title=The cryonics dilemma: will deep-frozen bodies be fit for new life?|last=Devlin|first=Hannah|date=2016-11-18|newspaper=the Guardian|language=en|access-date=2018-12-25|archive-date=2019-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124164111/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/nov/18/the-cryonics-dilemma-will-deep-frozen-bodies-be-fit-for-new-life|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=P5m4zNxaaSUC&pg=PA22&dq=cryonics+institute#v=onepage&q=cryonics%20institute&f=false|title=A Loose Canon: Essays on History, Modernity and Tradition|last=Coman|first=Brian J.|date=2007|publisher=Connor Court Publishing Pty Ltd|isbn=9780980293623|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/from-phyics-teacher-to-founder-of-the-cryonics-movement/2011/07/24/gIQAupuIXI_story.html|title=Robert Ettinger, founder of the cryonics movement, dies at 92|last=|first=|date=|website=Washington Post|language=en|access-date=2018-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216025735/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/from-phyics-teacher-to-founder-of-the-cryonics-movement/2011/07/24/gIQAupuIXI_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2010/01/facility_in_macomb_county_keep.html|title=Facility in Macomb County keeps bodies frozen in hopes of bringing them back to life|last=Press|first=The Associated|date=|website=MLive.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-25|archive-date=2011-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110426183955/http://www.mlive.com/news/detroit/index.ssf/2010/01/facility_in_macomb_county_keep.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==費用==
截止[[2016年3月|2016年3月]]，人體冷凍機構的會員收費為每年120美元，[[會員|會員]]亦可成為[[終身會員|終身會員]]，終身會員費用收費為1250美元。人體冷凍終身會員的全身人體冷凍服務及貯存的收費為28,000美元，非終身會員 （即年費會員） 則為35,000美元。另外，人體冷凍還設有隨時候命及運輸服務 （Standby and Transportation Services），收費則是88,000美元至95,000美元。<ref>[http://www.cryonics.org/membership/ Cryonics Institute (CI) Membership page] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cryonics.org/membership/ |date=20210119015041 }},於2020年5月25日查閱</ref>

==服務人數及會員人數==
直至2020年4月，人體冷凍機構共有1672名[[會員|會員]]，269名會員向暫停生命機構 (Suspended Animation, Inc.)簽下協議獲提供[[候命|候命]]及[[運輸|運輸]]服務。該會共有187人接受了人體冷凍保存服務，及有187隻[[寵物|寵物]]接受了冷凍保存服務。該會透過[[液態氮|液態氮]]保存了305個[[人體|人體]][[基因|基因]]樣本。此外，直至2014年11月，該機構也透過[[液態氮|液態氮]]保存了57個[[寵物|寵物]]基因[[樣本|樣本]]，並有562名會員己向人體冷凍機構簽下[[協議|協議]]，會在[[法律|法律]]上宣佈[[死亡|死亡]]後提供冷凍服務。<ref>[http://www.cryonics.org/resources/member-statistics   Cryonics Institute (CI) Member Statistics Details] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cryonics.org/resources/member-statistics |date=20200925085407 }},於2020年5月25日查閱</ref>

